column4: hi, can anyone tell any tips why bookmark syncing in firefox through ubuntuone is not working
i'm logged into ubuntuone (file are synced allright), bookmark syncing is on, and i have bindwood installed in firefox and enabled, yet the bookmarks don' get synced
on ubuntuone, i was asked to register the computer (probably for file sharing), but for tomboy-notes syncing i was asked again separately - i didn't got asked for bookmarks however..
Please don't flood, use http://paste.ubuntu.com to paste, don't use Enter as punctuation.
